cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with measuring visual similarity in image retrieval, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning networks as an approximation of non-metric similarity functions suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study of how these models generalize across different datasets indicates a concern with performance evaluation (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
